ns. For more than a century, it has embodied the nation’s best aspirations and-especially-its continuing faith in education itself.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aSchool buildingsxSocial aspectsxHistoryxUnited StatesxUnited States. 0aSchool buildingsxSocial aspectszUnited StatesxHistory. 7aHISTORY / United States / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015627040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300156270423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300156270/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles